<Content>Great value at Art Hotel Charlottenburg Hof Great value for families at the Art Hotel Charlottenburg Hof.Good points: clean, friendly, spacious rooms, computer with free internet access in each room.Bad points: No lift, small bathrooms.Best points. Location, just across the road from Charlottenburg S bahn station, easy access to all parts of the city with frequent trains.Value, super value for families 4 bedded room 59 euro per night if booked through hotel off peak times Oct - March.Friendly and stylish cafe next door Cafe Miro good coffee and breakfast. 
